  <amendments/>
  <summary>1/19/1999--Introduced.
Expand and Rebuild America's Schools Act of 1997 (sic) - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow a limited credit to eligible taxpayers holding school construction bonds. Defines such bonds. Establishes a private business contribution requirement for bond issuers. Defines as eligible taxpayers certain banks, insurance companies, and corporations. Sets a national school construction bond limit.</summary>
